OL,5, Five business groups have written to   
OL,6, Chancellor Rishi Sunak urging support  
OL,7, for businesses and consumers as energy 
OL,8, costs soar.                            
OL,10,FThe groups, representing small and     
OL,11,Flarge businesses, bosses and           
OL,12,Fmanufacturers, said price rises on the 
OL,13,Fhorizon could push millions of people  
OL,14,Finto fuel poverty.                     
OL,16,FThey said businesses had also been hit 
OL,17,Fby steep rises in bills.               
OL,19,FThe Treasury said it was helping       
OL,20,Ffamilies with #12bn support.           
